  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_129",
    "english": "Beastman. Settled in a corner of Yomihara at some point and seems to have become something of a mascot among the locals. Free-spirited and straightforward, she primarily thinks about eating, playing, and sleeping. Like a cat, she wanders her territory aimlessly, looking for food along the way.\n\nNot affiliated with any organization, she has fought against both Taimanins and UFS personnel. However, her nature leads her to treat battles as play and her enemies as playmates. True to her feline nature, she is swift, outmaneuvering her foes with physical abilities far beyond those of an ordinary human.",
    "japanese": "Beastman. Settled in a corner of Yomihara at some point and seems to have become something of a mascot among the locals. Free-spirited and straightforward, she primarily thinks about eating, playing, and sleeping. Like a cat, she wanders her territory aimlessly, looking for food along the way.\n\nNot affiliated with any organization, she has fought against both Taimanins and UFS personnel. However, her nature leads her to treat battles as play and her enemies as playmates. True to her feline nature, she is swift, outmaneuvering her foes with physical abilities far beyond those of an ordinary human.",
    "korean": "Beastman. Settled in a corner of Yomihara at some point and seems to have become something of a mascot among the locals. Free-spirited and straightforward, she primarily thinks about eating, playing, and sleeping. Like a cat, she wanders her territory aimlessly, looking for food along the way.\n\nNot affiliated with any organization, she has fought against both Taimanins and UFS personnel. However, her nature leads her to treat battles as play and her enemies as playmates. True to her feline nature, she is swift, outmaneuvering her foes with physical abilities far beyond those of an ordinary human.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Beastman. Settled in a corner of Yomihara at some point and seems to have become something of a mascot among the locals. Free-spirited and straightforward, she primarily thinks about eating, playing, and sleeping. Like a cat, she wanders her territory aimlessly, looking for food along the way.\n\nNot affiliated with any organization, she has fought against both Taimanins and UFS personnel. However, her nature leads her to treat battles as play and her enemies as playmates. True to her feline nature, she is swift, outmaneuvering her foes with physical abilities far beyond those of an ordinary human.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Beastman. Settled in a corner of Yomihara at some point and seems to have become something of a mascot among the locals. Free-spirited and straightforward, she primarily thinks about eating, playing, and sleeping. Like a cat, she wanders her territory aimlessly, looking for food along the way.\n\nNot affiliated with any organization, she has fought against both Taimanins and UFS personnel. However, her nature leads her to treat battles as play and her enemies as playmates. True to her feline nature, she is swift, outmaneuvering her foes with physical abilities far beyond those of an ordinary human.",
    "spanish": "Beastman. Settled in a corner of Yomihara at some point and seems to have become something of a mascot among the locals. Free-spirited and straightforward, she primarily thinks about eating, playing, and sleeping. Like a cat, she wanders her territory aimlessly, looking for food along the way.\n\nNot affiliated with any organization, she has fought against both Taimanins and UFS personnel. However, her nature leads her to treat battles as play and her enemies as playmates. True to her feline nature, she is swift, outmaneuvering her foes with physical abilities far beyond those of an ordinary human."
